A command is not NULL terminated and can contain NULL bytes.
Parameters
bufferPointer to the buffer in which the library should store the command
buffLenSize of the buffer
cmdLenPointer to an integer that will hold the actual size of the command
Returns
Error code (see eARCOMMANDS_GENERATOR_ERROR)
